\c 3
\s Ugobe lukaHamani lokubulala amaJuda
\p
\v 1 Emva kwalezizindaba inkosi uAhasuwerusi yamkhulisa uHamani indodana kaHamedatha\x + 5.11. 10.2.\x* umAgagi\x + 3.10. 8.3,5. 9.24. Nani 24.7. 1 Sam. 15.8.\x*, yamphakamisa, yabeka isihlalo sakhe phezu kwazo zonke iziphathamandla ezazilaye\x + 5.11. 10.2.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho zonke inceku zenkosi ezazisesangweni lenkosi zakhothama zamkhonza uHamani, ngoba inkosi yayilaye ngokunjalo ngaye. Kodwa uModekhayi kakhothamanga kakhonzanga\x + 2.19.\x*.
\v 3 Izinceku zenkosi ezazisesangweni lenkosi\x + 2.19.\x* zasezisithi kuModekhayi: Kungani useqa umlayo wenkosi\x + 3.2.\x*?
\v 4 Kwasekusithi zikhuluma laye insuku ngensuku, kodwa engazizwanga, zamtshela uHamani ukuze zibone ukuthi amazwi kaModekhayi azakuma yini; ngoba wayezitshelile ukuthi ungumJuda.
\v 5 UHamani esebonile ukuthi uModekhayi kakhothamanga njalo kakhonzanga kuye\x + 3.2. 5.9.\x*, uHamani wagcwala intukuthelo\x + Dan. 3.19.\x*.
\v 6 Wesedelela emehlweni akhe ukumthela isandla uModekhayi yedwa, ngoba babemtshelile abantu bakibo kaModekhayi, ngakho uHamani wadinga ukuchitha wonke amaJuda, ayesembusweni wonke kaAhasuwerusi, abantu bakibo kaModekhayi.
\p
\v 7 Ngenyanga yokuqala, eyinyanga uNisani\x + Neh. 2.1.\x*, ngomnyaka wetshumi lambili wenkosi uAhasuwerusi, baphosa iPuri\x + 9.24,26.\x*, eliyinkatho, phambi kukaHamani, kusukela osukwini kusiya osukwini, njalo kusukela enyangeni kusiya enyangeni yetshumi lambili\x + Hlu. 20.9.\x*, eyinyanga uAdari\x + Ezra 6.15.\x*.
\p
\v 8 UHamani wasesithi enkosini uAhasuwerusi: Kukhona abantu abathile abahlakazeke basabalala phakathi kwabantu ezabelweni zonke zombuso wakho; lemilayo yabo\x + Ezra 4.12,13. Seb. 16.20,21.\x* yehlukile kweyabo bonke abantu\x + 1.7.\x*, lemilayo yenkosi kabayenzi; ngakho kakufanelanga enkosini ukuthi ibayekele bahlale.
\v 9 Uba kulungile enkosini, kakubhalwe ukuthi bachithwe, njalo ngizalinganisa \w amathalenta\w** esiliva azinkulungwane ezilitshumi ezandleni zabenzi bomsebenzi, ukuze afakwe kokuligugu kwenkosi.
\v 10 Inkosi yasikhupha indandatho yophawu lwayo esandleni sayo, yayinika uHamani indodana kaHamedatha\x + 8.2. 3.12. 8.8,10. Gen. 41.42.\x* umAgagi\x + 3.10. 8.3,5. 9.24. Nani 24.7. 1 Sam. 15.8.\x*, isitha samaJuda.
\v 11 Inkosi yasisithi kuHamani: Isiliva usinikiwe, labantu, ukwenza ngabo njengokuhle emehlweni akho.
\v 12 Kwasekubizwa ababhali benkosi\x + 8.9.\x* ngenyanga yokuqala ngosuku lwetshumi lantathu lwayo\x + 3.7.\x*; kwasekubhalwa njengakho konke uHamani ayekulayile, ezikhulwini zenkosi\x + Ezra 8.36.\x* lakubabusi ababephezu kwesabelo lesabelo\x + 1 Kho. 10.15.\x*, lakuziphathamandla zesizwe lesizwe sesabelo lesabelo, njengokombhalo waso\x + 1.22. 8.9.\x*, labantu ngabantu ngokolimi lwabo; kwabhalwa ebizweni lenkosi uAhasuwerusi\x + 8.8,10. 1 Kho. 21.8.\x*, kwananyathiselwa ngendandatho yophawu lwenkosi.
\v 13 Incwadi zathunyelwa ngesandla sezigijimi\x + 8.10. 2 Lan. 30.6.\x* kuzo zonke izabelo zenkosi ukuchitha, ukubulala, lokubhubhisa wonke amaJuda, kusukela komutsha kusiya komdala, abantwanyana labesifazana\x + 7.4.\x*, ngasuku lunye\x + 8.12. 9.1.\x*, ngolwetshumi lantathu lwenyanga yetshumi lambili, eyinyanga uAdari\x + Ezra 6.15.\x*, lokuthi kuphangwe impahla yawo\x + 8.11.\x*.
\v 14 Ikhophi yombhalo yokuthi umlayo unikwe kuso sonke isabelo ngesabelo yayisobala kubo bonke abantu ukuze balungele lolosuku\x + 8.13,14.\x*.
\v 15 Izigijimi zaphuma ziphangisiswa yilizwi lenkosi\x + 8.10. 2 Lan. 30.6.\x*, lomthetho wanikwa eShushani isigodlo. Inkosi loHamani basebehlalela ukunatha, kodwa umuzi iShushani wawusanganisekile\x + 8.15. Eks. 14.3.\x*.